Package com.io7m.jspatial.quadtrees

Quadtree implementations.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    QuadrantType
    The type of quadrants in quadtrees.
    QuadTreeBuilderType<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A mutable builder for instantiating quadtree implementations.
    QuadTreeMemberType<T>
    The type of objects that can be placed into a quadtree.
    QuadTreeSDType<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    The interface provided by quadtree implementations that distinguish between static (immovable) and dynamic (movable) objects.
    QuadTreeTraversalType<E extends Throwable>
    The type of procedures used when iterating over quadrants in quadtrees.
    QuadTreeType<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    The interface provided by quadtree implementations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Quadrants
    Functions to produce new quadrants from an existing pair of corners.
    QuadTreeBasic<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    An extremely simple quadtree implementation.
    QuadTreeBuilder<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    The default implementation of the QuadTreeBuilderType.
    QuadTreeLimit<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implementation based on QuadTreeBasic but implementing a minimum size limit on quadrants.
    QuadTreePrune<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implementation based on QuadTreeBasic but implementing empty node pruning when an object is removed from the tree.
    QuadTreePruneLimit<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implement based on both QuadTreeLimit and QuadTreePrune.
    QuadTreeRaycastResult<T extends BoundingAreaType>
    An object returned by a successful raycast operation.
    QuadTreeSDBasic<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implementation based on QuadTreeBasic, but extended with the concept of static/dynamic categorization for inserted objects.
    QuadTreeSDLimit<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implementation based on QuadTreeSDBasic but implementing a minimum size limit on quadrants.
    QuadTreeSDPrune<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implementation based on QuadTreeSDBasic but implementing empty node pruning when an object is removed from the tree.
    QuadTreeSDPruneLimit<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
    A quadtree implement based on both QuadTreeSDLimit and QuadTreeSDPrune.
